d.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n細個無留心讀書拋錯書包 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都聽過<br />\n<br />\n君子遠庖廚 非奸即盗<br />\n<br />\n原來係真既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e4b2ca1990d87ae8024b6165f2b32b11d977e1","tid":221314,"uid":30845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:22:54.000Z","msg":"當分晒屍就冇老母生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你定多話佢噁心啫"},{"pid":"d8e26d6bc03496c574a208f0eb8ad236ba3a568c","tid":221314,"uid":53848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:24:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>on9 香港真係要學下日本 全班人養豬 之後劏左去 全班一齊食左佢 呢種生命教育真係有必要性 殺動物呢種所謂殘忍嘅事根本日日發生 將最殘忍果part掉比人做 自己坐享道德高地話返人地殘忍 除非你食素啦</blockquote><br />\n正想講呢個日本人嘅教育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實細細個就中會唔會有心理陰影，食自己養嘅豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2917d9a4ed49a38af41f328c1c44ce2698869463","tid":221314,"uid":41366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:24:19.000Z","msg":"咁戇㞗既野真係第一次聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ba5ce85c8d086e7da3e8873a31607847274a93","tid":221314,"uid":50018,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:26:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>藍屍肥媽竟然冇人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢件事唔關maria cordero政治取態事 (肥乜撚野媽，同佢有親咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n我地屌maria cordero 都要屌得啱，例如佢捐錢支持行私刑，而唔係因人廢言，更加要活用邏輯思辯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2656aabaa94f750cd79c57c4141728a1b0d334fc","tid":221314,"uid":59889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:26:59.000Z","msg":"不撚知所謂"},{"pid":"09609ecc9e5a39bd3de822d33013efc9b4a3565b","tid":221314,"uid":75525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:27:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無綫飲食節目《阿媽教落食平D》，做到第六輯，四年來長做長有，不少觀眾都很喜歡看肥媽和陸浩明的搞笑互動。不過其中一集兩人去凍肉店，成隻完整冰鮮乳豬攝入鏡，被批殘忍。<br />\n<br />\n節目第三集肥媽教煮豬仔骨、蠔仔和安格斯牛柳粒，與陸浩明一齊去凍肉店去買食材，期間拿起兩隻冰鮮乳豬，是眼耳口鼻都看得一清二楚的完整冰鮮乳豬，畫面令人毛管戙，引起觀眾反感。非牟利獸醫服務協會執行主席麥志豪就在社交網站發文，批評此節目「品味差」、「核突」，直指「飲食節目啫，唔好咁賤視生命啦！豬，都有阿媽生架！」<br />\n<br />\n不少網民都表示認同，留言表示覺得好核突、好不安，大罵「殘忍」、「人面獸心」，直指「食你就食，唔好揸住佢來舞啦！」其實節目第一輯都曾拍攝過燒孔豬畫面，當時都引起不少爭議。所謂眼不見為乾淨，就算不不是素食者，食落肚的肉都不會想看到令人不安的製作過程，難免令人反感。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n偽善L 去死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n又係非牟利柒頭麥志豪"},{"pid":"3e2928384cab0360bf969e1a57058c64c3047524","tid":221314,"uid":112813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:30:37.000Z","msg":"肥媽咁勁不如上hell's kitchen la<br />\n睇佢俾Gordon Ramsay 屌到上天<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a00b03e3dd9aae06dfd43d84ff87490c6fb3a98b","tid":221314,"uid":2111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:31:33.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n就咁睇幅圖係有少少反感<br />\n利申：非偽善道德撚"},{"pid":"260fa1993b4cd90026789500a1726515b17d7bf5","tid":221314,"uid":46950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T00:32:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>愈嚟愈覺得中國古代道德觀好有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜撚嘢<span style=\"color: red;\">君子遠疱廚</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i