就唔殘忍咩"},{"pid":"60290d34fc90e7546bd80d379bd74aca2bfcefae","tid":221314,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T01:22:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>話核突個D應該成世未落過街市<br />\n<br />\n其實魚多數都係原條上,鮑魚青口貝類乜都多數都係原隻上,魚生刺身直頭係生勾勾&hellip;<br />\n好L殘忍啊屌我老母！唔好賤視生命啊！放低條魚啊等我拯救善良ＧＥ人啦！</blockquote><br />\n宜家啲人真係好離地 戇撚鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n賤視生命<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n魚生條魚死咗"},{"pid":"4a318e01fa95daa3b231fc714eade9afff595c3c","tid":221314,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T01:47:08.000Z","msg":"大佬呀，你要食嘢就一定會殺咗個樣嘢架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依個係生態上嘅能量轉移，對食物仁慈先係對自己殘忍"},{"pid":"8e09ff9078f5332e3bdff29a12e09529c6542be3","tid":221314,"uid":5148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T01:47:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飲喜酒食乳豬就無問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n仆街仲唔上乳豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13baa875034efc6368461bdb1ab2e437330ae89e","tid":221314,"uid":35315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T01:48:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on9 隻野死咗 你食既豬咪又係來自佢地 只係斬開咗 斬開咗就唔殘忍咩</blockquote><br />\n證明好多溫室小花，淨係識得食個下"},{"pid":"a0e3cbc79487403e4d1b2bb1673139ae0e859aa3","tid":221314,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T01:48:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/10YG6Rf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F10YG6Rf.jpg&h=1572a277&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9O3mBV6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9O3mBV6.jpg&h=ea91c1e2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/29/094811_26f4b6107b7019450a8d8214847ffb75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F29%2F094811_26f4b6107b7019450a8d8214847ffb75.jpg&h=9d64d3ce&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f800d6c752433d2edcac7ccb4eaa0ff2203685ae","tid":221314,"uid":30487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T01:56:13.000Z","msg":"左膠去死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6b9192e692479e8983076673e32df957050934","tid":221314,"uid":32063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:00:18.000Z","msg":"食豬肉牛肉個陣，唔當食緊既野曾經係一條生命，先係最賤視生命"},{"pid":"6a2e0c5da538c863ab6f051ec4a5a41ae014c5f3","tid":221314,"uid":93753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:05:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食豬肉牛肉個陣，唔當食緊既野曾經係一條生命，先係最賤視生命</blockquote><br />\n正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 珍視生命就係要由衷感激小動物為我們付出生命去成為我地既食物。所以不能浪費食物<br />\n<br />\n當然食素就更能體現愛惜所有生命"},{"pid":"e7986f96005bdd44a0a6f7a06c8002cdfee96963","tid":221314,"uid":1712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:50:44.000Z","msg":"見過剝田雞皮未？<br />\n見到係咪要報警？"},{"pid":"d4337e06cc315593f95ac8de9e233bb0c9c458f4","tid":221314,"uid":55568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:52:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食豬肉牛肉個陣，唔當食緊既野曾經係一條生命，先係最賤視生命</blockquote><br />\n所以日本食飯前句いただきます係好有意思<br />\n呢句唔係解我食飯啦<br />\n要係用敬語講我收下了<br />\n收左咩？咪食物嘅生命囉"},{"pid":"73fd47bad758916a173734a3c855f91d5d428f6d","tid":221314,"uid":1789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T02:59:45.000Z","msg":"植物無生命既？<br />\n你又知植物比你食個時唔痛既<br />\n餓撚死佢算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfe75eb6286f2539f3b1ee47a6869ceb5e60fc6a","tid":221314,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T03:02:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食豬肉牛肉個陣，唔當食緊既野曾經係一條生命，先係最賤視生命</blockquote><br />\n好同意<br />\n每個人食肉既時候其實都係體現緊大自然弱肉強食既精神<br />\n同獅子食山羊冇分別<br />\n講君子遠庖廚既人以為自己睇唔到血淋淋既畫面，就比其他肉食獸高尚"},{"pid":"389d75786db845231dd9e2bf57717d78ce042386","tid":221314,"uid":95096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T03:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁多人撐肥媽"},{"pid":"9d76fa37232d80f5ce404300d0da8d48c75ad963","tid":221314,"uid":98143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T03:08:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>班友平時去街巿咪打晒冷震?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n諗起個單新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71d54aa6cf11bc4b5f52a71c249900bebec86c91","tid":221314,"uid":112198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T03:47:24.000Z","msg":"人要生存就喺剝奪緊其他資源同生命<br />\n偽善L吔翻自己算啦 自體循環呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a986024989ee52c137e6e00d86d7fb2f9c6dc118","tid":221314,"uid":38739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T03:53:06.000Z","msg":"花生醬仲殘忍啦, 一粒粒花生壓到變成一PAT嘢, 佢哋被壓榨既過程嗰種掙扎比起原隻乳豬更痛苦"},{"pid":"aa3d333ed73175bd2bbe129bc11ccbe833dcfe83","tid":221314,"uid":27688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:53:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>花生醬仲殘忍啦, 一粒粒花生壓到變成一PAT嘢, 佢哋被壓榨既過程嗰種掙扎比起原隻乳豬更痛苦</blockquote><br />\n你做過花生又做過乳豬呀？"},{"pid":"4781b76f1bde4e0f135a8da841389c6c0823482e","tid":221314,"uid":26445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T04:55:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>花生醬仲殘忍啦, 一粒粒花生壓到變成一PAT嘢, 佢哋被壓榨既過程嗰種掙扎比起原隻乳豬更痛苦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1d731a0990d2f2ffb1f69d6f36c1cbbd52ff151","tid":221314,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T05:04:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無綫飲食節目《阿媽教落食平D》，做到第六輯，四年來長做長有，不少觀眾都很喜歡看肥媽和陸浩明的搞笑互動。不過其中一集兩人去凍肉店，成隻完整冰鮮乳豬攝入鏡，被批殘忍。<br />\n<br />\n節目第三集肥媽教煮豬仔骨、蠔仔和安格斯牛柳粒，與陸浩明一齊去凍肉店去買食材，期間拿起兩隻冰鮮乳豬，是眼耳口鼻都看得一清二楚的完整冰鮮乳豬，畫面令人毛管戙，引起觀眾反感。<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">非牟利獸醫服務協會執行主席麥志豪</span></span>就在社交網站發文，批評此節目「品味差」、「核突」，直指「飲食節目啫，唔好咁賤視生命啦！豬，都有阿媽生架！」<br />\n<br />\n不少網民都表示認同，留言表示覺得好核突、好不安，大罵「殘忍」、「人面獸心」，直指「食你就食，唔好揸住佢來舞啦！」其實節目第一輯都曾拍攝過燒孔豬畫面，當時都引起不少爭議。所謂眼不見為乾淨，就算不不是素食者，食落肚的肉都不會想看到令人不安的製作過程，難免令人反感。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n偽善L 去死啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7707eecbd205d5355a849b3df52bb1e8f07e9111","tid":221314,"uid":4867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T05:17:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁多人撐肥媽</blockquote><br />\n唔關政治事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c8dc61776dec7ef52ef87e00892029616c44a5","tid":221314,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-29T05:40:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/4-%E5%A8%9B%E5%9C%88%E4%BA%8B/2000523-%E8%82%A5%E5%AA%BD%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E4%B9%B3%E8%B1%AC%E5%85%A5%E9%8F%A1%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%B9%E6%AE%98%E5%BF%8D%EF%BC%9A%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E8%B3%A4%E8%A6%96%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD?r=w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bastillepost.com%2Fhongkong%2F4-%25E5%25A8%259B%25E5%259C%2588%25E4%25BA%258B%2F2000523-%25E8%2582%25A5%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E7%25AF%2580%25E7%259B%25AE%25E4%25B9%25B3%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%258F%25A1%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%2589%25B9%25E6%25AE%2598%25E5%25BF%258D%25EF%25BC%259A%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25A5%25BD%25E8%25B3%25A4%25E8%25A6%2596%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2591%25BD%3Fr%3Dw&d=o%2BIu8jl9TkUz6xxK8T5I2%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=0734bbdb\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/4-%E5%A8%9B%E5%9C%88%E4%BA%8B/2000523-%E8%82%A5%E5%AA%BD%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E4%B9%B3%E8%B1%AC%E5%85%A5%E9%8F%A1%E8%A2%AB%E6%89%B9%E6%AE%98%E5%BF%8D%EF%BC%9A%E5%94%94%E5%A5%BD%E8%B3%A4%E8%A6%96%E7%94%9F%E5%91%BD?r=w</a></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌，巴士的報，狗都唔睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食屎的報<br />\n食屎先睇"}]}